-{"id":"wa-0go.6","title":"Natural language CLI output: integrate templates into all CLI commands","description":"# Natural language CLI output

## Purpose
Integrate natural language templates into all CLI output so users see human-readable descriptions everywhere.

## Integration Points

### 1. wa events Command
```bash
wa events

# Before (technical)
Event: codex.usage_limit_warning
Time: 2026-01-18T14:32:05Z
Pane: 0

# After (natural language)
╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
│ Recent Events                                                              │
├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 14:32  Codex at 85% of daily limit                                        │
